, a war that we'd already surrendered to, outfoxed by the prevailing methods of digital control: self-surveillance and willing surrender of our privacy and some of our lesser freedoms, caught in an increasingly elaborate state of exception.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999997903405748, \"rank\": 2.0905687239587255e-07, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this technological hyper\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"revolution\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"a war\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the prevailing methods\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"digital control\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"self-surveillance\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"willing surrender\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"our privacy\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"our lesser freedoms\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"an increasingly elaborate state\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"exception\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's historic role in the spread and ubiquity of surveillance rivals its prestigious cuisine.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"France's historic role\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the spread\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"ubiquity\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"its prestigious cuisine\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Surveillance\\\" is a French word, after all.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5584021746673479, \"rank\": 0.3471032663586899, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surveillance\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 11th century, this emerged in the restructuring of the city, leading the mid-1700s' invention of the urban fortress.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 11th century\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"the restructuring\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"the mid-1700s' invention\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"the urban fortress\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Law enforcement had figured out how to spy.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Law enforcement\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Napoleon was the first to use aerial surveillance - a new kind of espionage.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.743368185822612e-35, \"text\": \"Napoleon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aerial surveillance\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"a new kind\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"espionage\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly, warfare was secretive.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"warfare\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Invisible.\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Military violence became clandestine, the task of secret police, an \\\"army of the interior.\\\"\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Military violence\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"secret police\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"army\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the interior\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its weapons were surveillance and disinformation.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its weapons\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The war could take place behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The war\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody even had to know who was fighting.\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a game the elites could play on their own but through society.\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"the elites\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This marks a shift from passive surveillance to active, AI-driven mass surveillance.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shift\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"passive surveillance\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3480}, {\"ngram\": \"active, AI-driven mass surveillance\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Modern warfare is about depriving the enemy.\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modern warfare\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3536}, {\"ngram\": \"the enemy\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Containing its movement.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its movement\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ability to move is the mark of freedom.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ability\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"the mark\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3623}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is part of the reason governments often want to centralize.\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"governments\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a funny connection between surveillance and disinformation.\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a funny connection\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3729}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We like to think that surveillance is designed to get rid of disinformation.\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In reality, surveillance and disinformation are like two con men pretending to fight.\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"two con men\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are both working for intelligence agencies and secret services.\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"intelligence agencies\", \"from\": 3961, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"secret services\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their job is to confuse us.\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their job\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To make us dumb.\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To believe in the right illusion.\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right illusion\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are supposed to feel tired and outraged.The funny thing about disinformation is that it's a counterattack.\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The funny thing\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4162}, {\"ngram\": \"a counterattack\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an assault on truth.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an assault\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4208}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a way to silence.\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in order to work, intelligence elites have to know what we think, feel, and believe.\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4254}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligence elites\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Modern wartime always leads to a flood of propaganda, especially in the social media era.\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modern wartime\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4346}, {\"ngram\": \"a flood\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"propaganda\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4384}, {\"ngram\": \"the social media era\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"War is when the elites put all their knowledge of propaganda to use.\", \"from\": 4422, \"to\": 4490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"War\", \"from\": 4422, \"to\": 4425}, {\"ngram\": \"the elites\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4444}, {\"ngram\": \"all their knowledge\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"propaganda\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surveillance is how we lose our privacy and our personal information.\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surveillance\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4503}, {\"ngram\": \"our privacy\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4530}, {\"ngram\": \"our personal information\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our information gives the powerful people even more power.\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our information\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4576}, {\"ngram\": \"the powerful people\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"even more power\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Intelligence agencies use that information to make disinformation.\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Intelligence agencies\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"that information\", \"from\": 4646, \"to\": 4662}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Worse, they are doing it all right before our eyes.\", \"from\": 4687, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our eyes\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It turns out that Big Brother is not monitoring us, because we are doing all the work for him.\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Big Brother\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4769}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4790}, {\"ngram\": \"all the work\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are experts at self-surveillance.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4850}, {\"ngram\": \"self-surveillance\", \"from\": 4854, \"to\": 4871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do it with a smile.\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the sake of convenience, we surrender our privacy and some of our freedoms.\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sake\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"convenience\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4923}, {\"ngram\": \"our privacy\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 4949}, {\"ngram\": \"our freedoms\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the while, a new totalitarianism is on the rise.\", \"from\": 4976, \"to\": 5028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new totalitarianism\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 5012}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 5019, \"to\": 5027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our future is a world of surveillance.\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our future\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5039}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonstop surveillance.\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nonstop surveillance\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More and more, we will be watched, scanned, monitored, ranked, punished, spied on, and evaluated.\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin Ryan Staff Writer\", \"from\": 5189, \"to\": 5213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5189, \"end\": 5199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_P._Ryan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3465145733725927e-14, \"text\": \"Kevin Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_P._Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_P._Ryan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"